SUMMARY:Information: ELIZABETH LINE: Sunday 15 March\, from 0745\, a 
 reduced service operates between Paddington and Maidenhead / Heathrow. Two
  trains an hour serve Heathrow Terminal 4\, West Drayton\, Langley\, 
 Slough\, Burnham and Maidenhead. Four trains an hour serve Heathrow 
 Terminals 2 & 3. Six trains an hour serve Ealing Broadway\, Southall and 
 Hayes & Harlington. No trains will call at Acton Main Line\, West Ealing 
 and Hanwell.
END:VEVENT
